cross: Dendrobium Cleopatra x Dendrobium Burana Pearl
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Thirty-six brilliantly feathered flowers on three inflorescences up to 35 cm; sepals ovate-acuminate, white brushed fuchsia purple; petals broadly rhomboid, white overlaid and brushed fuchsia purple; lip white overlaid fuchsia purple, keels feathered; column white, anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
